1. *Smirite* se, molim vas! (Settle down, please!)
2. Ona je uzela *smirite* da bi se smirila. (She took a sedative to calm down.)
3. *Smirite* se i ne ljutite se. (Calm down and don't get angry.)
4. Ne mogu da *smirim* vetar. (I can't calm the wind.)
5. On se nada da će njegove reči *smiriti* njegovu ženu. (He hopes his words will calm his wife down.)